    "title": "京东规则动态一览（2025年9月8日-2025年9月12日）",
    "followRuleId": "1282637201976463360",
    "content": "<p style=\"margin: 0cm; line-height: 200%; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">【规则公示】</span></strong></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; line-height: 200%; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">1</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">、【新增】</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\"><a style=\"color: #467886; text-decoration: underline;\" href=\"https://learn-jdm.jd.com/knowledge/rule/detail?ruleId=1283643387106430976\">《京东开放平台个人/个体店个护健康品类销售激励政策》</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; line-height: 200%; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">核心内容：</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">当商家2025年9月销售GMV对比8月增长达到阶梯目标时，即可获得不同比例的扣点返还。</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; line-height: 200%; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">2</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">、【新增】</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\"><a style=\"color: #467886; text-decoration: underline;\" href=\"https://learn-jdm.jd.com/knowledge/rule/detail?ruleId=1282213162308997120\">《2025年国庆节期间延迟结算公告》</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; line-height: 200%; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">核心内容：</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">2025</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">年9月30日至10月8日期间的交易将在2025年10月9日统一结算。</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; line-height: 200%; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">【规则生效】</span></strong></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; line-height: 200%; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">1</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">、【新增】</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\"><a style=\"color: #467886; text-decoration: underline;\" href=\"https://learn-jdm.jd.com/knowledge/rule/detail?ruleId=1279994337958170624\">《京东开放平台显卡类目招商激励政策》&nbsp;</a></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; line-height: 200%; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">核心内容：</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">激励周期内，显卡类目商家达成GMV目标要求，可获得一定比例的运营支持服务费返还。</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; line-height: 200%; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">2</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">、【新增】</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\"><a style=\"color: #467886; text-decoration: underline;\" href=\"https://learn-jdm.jd.com/knowledge/rule/detail?ruleId=1279999657648459776\">《京东开放平台个人/个体店厨房小电品类销售激励政策》</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; line-height: 200%; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">核心内容：</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">激励周期内，厨房小电类目商家达成GMV目标且满足环比增长要求，可享受对应GMV阶梯扣点折扣。</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; line-height: 200%; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">3</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">、【新增】</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\"><a style=\"color: #467886; text-decoration: underline;\" href=\"https://learn-jdm.jd.com/knowledge/rule/detail?ruleId=1280395865961402368\">《京东开放平台个人/个体店粮油调味品类激励政策》</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; line-height: 200%; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">核心内容：</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">激励周期内，粮油调味类目指定品牌商家达成GMV目标且满足环比增长要求，可享受对应GMV阶梯扣点折扣。</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; line-height: 200%; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">4</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">、【新增】</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\"><a style=\"color: #467886; text-decoration: underline;\" href=\"https://learn-jdm.jd.com/knowledge/rule/detail?ruleId=1281122398384558080\">《京东开放平台个人个体店玩具乐器-积木拼插类目销售激励政策》</a></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; line-height: 200%; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">核心内容：</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">激励周期内，积木拼插类目商家达成GMV目标要求，可获得现金形式一定比例的扣点返回。</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; line-height: 200%; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">5</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">、【修订】</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\"><a style=\"color: #467886; text-decoration: underline;\" href=\"https://learn-jdm.jd.com/knowledge/rule/detail?ruleId=1281216148016336896\">《京东开放平台个人店铺主体升级规则》&nbsp;</a></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; line-height: 200%; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">核心内容：</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">当前仅支持个人升级为个体工商户，调整为支持个人升级为个体工商户或企业以及由个体工商户升级为企业。</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; line-height: 200%; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">6</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">、【修订】</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\"><a style=\"color: #467886; text-decoration: underline;\" href=\"https://learn-jdm.jd.com/knowledge/rule/detail?ruleId=1280000031730044928\">《京东开放平台非全新商品管理规则》</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; line-height: 200%; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">核心内容：</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">①调整非全新商品定义：非全新商品包括官翻机、展机、样机等；②新增对于非全新商品类目挂靠要求及对应类目乱挂违规处理措施。</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; line-height: 200%; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">7</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">、【修订】</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\"><a style=\"color: #467886; text-decoration: underline;\" href=\"https://learn-jdm.jd.com/knowledge/rule/detail?ruleId=1280069295098957824\">《京东开放平台不当发布商品或信息细则》&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</a></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; line-height: 200%; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">核心内容：</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">①细化类目乱挂的范围；②调整类目乱挂的违规处理措施。</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; line-height: 200%; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">8</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">、【修订】</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\"><a style=\"color: #467886; text-decoration: underline;\" href=\"https://learn-jdm.jd.com/knowledge/rule/detail?ruleId=1280860341454114816\">《京东开放平台发布混淆信息细则》</a></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; line-height: 200%; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">核心内容：</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">①调整混淆信息的定义；②调整混淆信息的违规处理措施；③补充规则解读。</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; line-height: 200%; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">9</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">、【新增】</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\"><a style=\"color: #467886; text-decoration: underline;\" href=\"https://learn-jdm.jd.com/knowledge/rule/detail?ruleId=1280852326801870848\">《京东开放平台假冒品牌细则》</a></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; line-height: 200%; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">核心内容：</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">明确假冒品牌定义：商家在商品发布、销售、售后等阶段可能导致消费者对商品品牌产生认知偏差的行为，及违规处理措施。</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; line-height: 200%; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">10</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">、【修订】</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\"><a style=\"color: #467886; text-decoration: underline;\" href=\"https://learn-jdm.jd.com/knowledge/rule/detail?ruleId=1280846900215549952\">《京东开放平台出售假冒商品细则》</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; line-height: 200%; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">核心内容：</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">①调整假冒商品的定义；②调整假冒商品的违规处理措施；③补充规则解读。</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; line-height: 200%; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">11</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">、【修订】</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\"><a style=\"color: #467886; text-decoration: underline;\" href=\"https://learn-jdm.jd.com/knowledge/rule/detail?ruleId=1280880991510073344\">《京东开放平台个人/个体合规管理规则》</a></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; line-height: 200%; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">核心内容：</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">①调整出售假冒商品和发布混淆信息的定义及处理措施。②新增出售假冒品牌的定义及处理措施，删除品牌欺诈场景。</span></p>",
